_track.png&h=a2575b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荷貝 1979年<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">其殘餘部份繼續向西移動，\n為中南半島北部帶來大雨，\n穿越越南、寮國、緬甸、孟加拉後再進入海面，\n在孟加拉灣近恆河口淺岸處再次增強為一氣旋風暴（熱帶風暴）</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7cd34a51bfd99e667e9095cc339b3bdfd02a5364","tid":2152982,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"熱帶低氣壓不等於颱風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21828ee284ba6bde0792121f9bed90735d0f56f0","tid":2152982,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"要睇地勢<br />\n華南一帶無乜高山<br />\n<br />\n台灣有玉山 3,952米（12,967英尺）<br />\n菲律賓Mount Pulag 2,922米（9,587英尺）"},{"pid":"9abe26f652e9b0b271cd48f23bc484136206b936","tid":2152982,"uid":361025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ea7e14c03ee4e80b3c0a057175fec346d805843","tid":2152982,"uid":262621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"屌,都未登陸"}]}